overview: In this sexually charged "mockumentary", we follow the exploits of a slightly deceptive headhunter, Natalie (Brooklyn Chase), who finds highly qualified people - 'less than' quality jobs. Whether it's a Babysitter, French Maid, Vacuum Salesman or Student Mover, all of the candidates bend over backwards to do their deeds! Odd Jobs because everyone deserves a raise!
title: Odd Jobs
